        <p class="text-lg mb-6">
          Interior waterproofing typically costs 40-60% less than exterior solutions while providing excellent protection. 
          Most Toronto homes invest $8,000-$15,000 for complete interior systems, with costs varying based on basement size and complexity.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8">
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Small Basement</h4>
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">$8,000-$12,000</p>
            <p class="text-sm opacity-80">Under 1,000 sq ft</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Average Basement</h4>
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">$12,000-$18,000</p>
            <p class="text-sm opacity-80">1,000-1,500 sq ft</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-lg p-6 text-center">
            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Large Basement</h4>
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary mb-2">$18,000-$25,000</p>
            <p class="text-sm opacity-80">Over 1,500 sq ft</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <CalloutBox type="tip" title="Financing Available">
          <p>0% financing for 12 months, extended payment plans available. Many clients also take advantage of city rebates and insurance claim assistance.</p>
        </CalloutBox>
      </div>
    </ContentSection>

    <!-- FAQ Section -->
    <ContentSection 
      title="Frequently Asked Questions"
      variant="gradient"
      centered
    >
      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        <QuestionAnswer 
          question="How effective is interior waterproofing compared to exterior?"
          variant="card"
        >
          <p>Interior waterproofing is highly effective for managing water that reaches your foundation. While exterior systems prevent water entry, interior systems excel at collecting and removing water that does penetrate. Our systems remove 99.9% of water and come with lifetime warranties.</p>
        </QuestionAnswer>

        <QuestionAnswer 
          question="Will installation damage my finished basement?"
          variant="card"
        >
          <p>We specialize in working with finished basements using precise cutting techniques that preserve most finishes. Typically, we only need to remove the bottom 2 feet of wall finishes, and we can often save flooring with careful planning.</p>
        </QuestionAnswer>

        <QuestionAnswer 
          question="How long does interior waterproofing last?"
          variant="card"
        >
          <p>Properly installed interior waterproofing systems last 30+ years with minimal maintenance. Our systems use commercial-grade components and come with lifetime transferable warranties on workmanship.</p>
        </QuestionAnswer>

        <QuestionAnswer 
          question="Can interior systems handle heavy rainfall?"
          variant="card"
        >
          <p>Absolutely. Our systems are designed for Toronto's extreme weather, including heavy spring runoff and intense summer storms. High-capacity sump pumps with battery backup ensure protection even during power outages.</p>
        </QuestionAnswer>
      </div>
    </ContentSection>

    <!-- Success Story -->
    <ContentSection 
      variant="dark"
      title="Recent Success Story"
      backgroundImage="/pics/testimonials/interior-waterproofing-bg.jpg"
      overlayOpacity={0.7}
      fullWidth
      centered
    >
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-xl italic mb-6">
          "Our finished basement was constantly damp despite exterior waterproofing attempts. DrySpace's interior system solved the problem completely. 
          The installation was clean, professional, and we've had zero moisture issues for three years now."
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg">— Michael R., North York</p>
        <div class="mt-6">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-yellow-400">
            <Star className="h-5 w-5 fill-yellow-400" />
            <Star className="h-5 w-5 fill-yellow-400" />
            <Star className="h-5 w-5 fill-yellow-400" />
            <Star className="h-5 w-5 fill-yellow-400" />
            <Star className="h-5 w-5 fill-yellow-400" />
            <span class="text-white ml-2">5.0 on Google Reviews</span>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </ContentSection>

    <!-- Emergency CTA -->
    <CalloutBox 
      type="emergency" 
      title="Basement Flooding Emergency?"
      animate={true}
    >
      <p>Don't wait for water damage to worsen. Our emergency team responds 24/7 throughout the GTA with temporary solutions and permanent repairs.</p>
      <p class="mt-4"><strong>Emergency Hotline: (437) 545-0067</strong> - Average response time: 2 hours</p>
    </CalloutBox>

    <!-- Related Services -->
    <ServiceLinks 
      title="Related Services & Resources"
      subtitle="Complete basement water management solutions"
      links={relatedResources}
      variant="featured"
      showImages={true}
    />

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <ContentSection 
      variant="gradient"
      title="Protect Your Basement Today"
      subtitle="Professional interior waterproofing with lifetime warranty"
      centered
      fullWidth
    >
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-center">
        <p class="text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Don't let water damage threaten your home's value and your family's health. 
          Our proven interior waterproofing systems provide reliable, long-term protection.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="/contact/" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-white bg-primary rounded-full shadow-xl hover:bg-primary/90 transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5">
            Get Free Assessment
          </a>
          <a href="tel:437-545-0067" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-bold text-primary bg-white rounded-full shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all hover:-translate-y-0.5">
            <Phone className="h-5 w-5 mr-2" />
            (437) 545-0067
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm opacity-80">
          Free consultation • Same-day quotes • Licensed & insured • Lifetime warranty
        </p>
      </div>
    </ContentSection>

  </ServiceMainContent>
</ServicePageTemplateV4>